compatible with all the different app

00:00:11.472 --> 00:00:14.080
stores out there, but
before you work too hard,

00:00:14.080 --> 00:00:16.990
you may want to start with focusing
on the best app store for your needs.

00:00:16.990 --> 00:00:21.450
Now think about your audience and
what they're more likely to use.

00:00:21.450 --> 00:00:23.990
Read the market share research
to validate your assumption.

