requirements to launching.

00:00:42.770 --> 00:00:45.050
These things change over time,
so the best thing for

00:00:45.050 --> 00:00:47.620
you to do is check out
their documentation.

00:00:47.620 --> 00:00:49.910
We've linked to various stores
in the instructor notes.

00:00:50.980 --> 00:00:54.310
